matplotlib is a Python package. It can be used after installing by importing in Python:

    import matplotlib
    import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

For C++ applications using matplotlib-cpp, add the following to your CMakeLists.txt:

    find_package(Python3 COMPONENTS Interpreter Development REQUIRED)
    find_package(matplotlib-cpp CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE matplotlib-cpp::matplotlib-cpp Python3::Python)
